inaugural address "A Call to Youth" by Mr.Chen Duxiu.
[Zhou Enlai, styled Xiang Yu, Nankai School Student]

557
00:23:43,980 --> 00:23:45,700
It was like a bright lamp

558
00:23:45,900 --> 00:23:46,980
that illuminated my mind,

559
00:23:47,180 --> 00:23:48,380
It made me feel like

560
00:23:48,580 --> 00:23:50,780
everything I've thought and learned and done before

561
00:23:50,980 --> 00:23:52,460
was all for nought.

562
00:23:52,740 --> 00:23:55,100
Therefore, I plan to switch

563
00:23:55,140 --> 00:23:56,500
my oral reading

564
00:23:56,540 --> 00:23:58,180
with this issue of "Youth Magazine"

565
00:23:58,420 --> 00:24:01,100
to share my delight with everyone.

566
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:08,060
Compariots desiring to leave the age of ignorance,

567
00:24:08,380 --> 00:24:10,340
ashamed of their simple mindedness,

568
00:24:10,460 --> 00:24:12,220
and eager to catch up,

569
00:24:12,580 --> 00:24:14,980
must pay equal attention to scientific knowledge and human rights.

570
00:24:15,260 --> 00:24:16,620
Our scholars do not know science.

571
00:24:16,980 --> 00:24:19,940
So they follow the Naturalists' School of auspicious signs and five elements.

572
00:24:20,140 --> 00:24:21,140
Confusing the world and cheating the people.

573
00:24:21,860 --> 00:24:23,140
Our farmers do not know science.

574
00:24:23,380 --> 00:24:25,140
So they have no methods for seed selection or insecticide.

575
00:24:25,380 --> 00:24:26,740
Our industrialists do not know science.

576
00:24:26,940 --> 00:24:28,740
So goods lie wasted on the ground,

577
00:24:28,980 --> 00:24:30,140
as we are dependent on foreign countries.

578
00:24:30,380 --> 00:24:31,900
Our merchants do not know science.

579
00:24:32,060 --> 00:24:34,260
So they only care about short term profits,

580
00:24:34,460 --> 00:24:37,300
without any thought for planning for the future.

581
00:24:37,620 --> 00:24:38,940
Our physicians do not know science.

582
00:24:39,380 --> 00:24:41,540
So they are not acquainted with human anatomy.

583
00:24:41,660 --> 00:24:42,380
The truth

584
00:24:42,420 --> 00:24:43,660
in the universe is boundless.

585
00:24:43,900 --> 00:24:46,980
The fertile realms of science awaiting the trailblazer

586
00:24:47,300 --> 00:24:48,260
are immense!

587
00:24:48,660 --> 00:24:50,580
Youth, take up the task!

588
00:24:51,580 --> 00:24:53,540
[Shanghai]

589
00:24:54,260 --> 00:24:56,180
Strike your little gong.

590
00:24:56,500 --> 00:24:58,540
"Youth Magazine" has been published.

591
00:24:58,780 --> 00:25:00,940
Chinese society has many difficulties.

592
00:25:01,180 --> 00:25:04,380
Mr. Chen Duxiu has shared two prescriptions with the public.

593
00:25:04,660 --> 00:25:06,860
Mr. Democracy and Mr. Science

594
00:25:07,100 --> 00:25:09,260
has already come to China.

595
00:25:09,460 --> 00:25:11,860
King of steel, Carnegie.

596
00:25:12,140 --> 00:25:13,620
That's Carnegie, not Shmarnegie.

597
00:25:13,780 --> 00:25:15,980
Wonderful! Wonderful!

598
00:25:16,060 --> 00:25:20,540
Turns out he was originally just a working boy.

599
00:25:20,620 --> 00:25:22,260
Great!

600
00:25:25,380 --> 00:25:26,340
Hello, excuse me.

601
00:25:26,660 --> 00:25:28,060
Take a look, take a peek.

602
00:25:28,100 --> 00:25:29,260
"Youth Magazine"

603
00:25:29,700 --> 00:25:31,700
Mr. Democracy and Mr. Science are here.

604
00:25:32,300 --> 00:25:35,140
See how Carnegie fulfilled the American Dream.

605
00:25:35,340 --> 00:25:37,840
How he went from a worker to the king of steel!

606
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:39,700
Here, take a look.

607
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:47,660
"Youth Magazine" Come, take a look.
Newest edition.

608
00:25:47,700 --> 00:25:48,500
Take a look.

609
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:49,660
Together?

610
00:25:50,460 --> 00:25:51,820
Thank you, thank you.

611
00:25:52,220 --> 00:25:53,020
"Youth Magazine"

612
00:25:54,060 --> 00:25:55,700
He's from my hometown.

613
00:25:55,740 --> 00:25:56,740
His name is Hu Shi.

614
00:25:57,260 --> 00:25:58,740
When he was nineteen years old

615
00:25:58,940 --> 00:26:00,220
he went to study abroad in the US,

616
00:26:00,260 --> 00:26:03,020
first at Cornell University to study agricultural science,

617
00:26:03,180 --> 00:26:05,260
then he switched his major to literature.

618
00:26:05,740 --> 00:26:08,740
He went to Columbia University this year

619
00:26:08,980 --> 00:26:11,300
to study with that well-known professor, John Dewey,

620
00:26:11,460 --> 00:26:13,540
for a doctorate of philosophy.

621
00:26:13,820 --> 00:26:15,140
It can be said that this child

622
00:26:15,300 --> 00:26:16,860
is proficient in literature, history, and philosophy.

623
00:26:17,340 --> 00:26:19,660
He saw an issue of our "Youth Magazine"
[Yi Baisha, styled Yue Cun, New Culture Movement activist]

624
00:26:19,940 --> 00:26:20,900
and was very excited.

625
00:26:21,060 --> 00:26:22,460
He's sent a letter

626
00:26:22,460 --> 00:26:25,360
and wants to write an article regarding the revolution in literature.

627
00:26:25,660 --> 00:26:28,460
So I would like to solicit your opinions.

628
00:26:32,300 --> 00:26:33,620
That's great!

629
00:26:35,220 --> 00:26:39,020
This topic of literary revolution is great.

630
00:26:39,020 --> 00:26:40,100
I really didn't expect

631
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:42,620
a student who has been overseas for years

632
00:26:42,740 --> 00:26:45,400
to be capable of seeing the purpose of my magazine

633
00:26:46,100 --> 00:26:47,180
so incisively.

634
00:26:47,660 --> 00:26:48,620
Genius!

635
00:26:50,020 --> 00:26:50,980
A kindred spirit!

636
00:26:51,860 --> 00:26:52,380
Alright, Zhong Fu

637
00:26:52,420 --> 00:26:53,180
A sworn friend!

638
00:26:53,460 --> 00:26:54,460
That's enough.

639
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:57,060
Zhong Fu, a young man's letter

640
00:26:57,100 --> 00:26:58,460
can get you so excited?

641
00:26:58,500 --> 00:26:59,500
Aren't you too ridiculous?

642
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:00,780
Not by half!

643
00:27:00,780 --> 00:27:03,140
Ideological guidance cannot be idle chit-chat,

644
00:27:03,140 --> 00:27:04,420
but start from a concrete basis

645
00:27:04,580 --> 00:27:05,940
that focuses on the lives of the masses.

646
00:27:06,220 --> 00:27:07,700
"Literary Revolution: A Tentative Proposal"

647
00:27:07,980 --> 00:27:09,700
If this article is written properly,

648
00:27:10,420 --> 00:27:11,500
it will be a bombshell!

649
00:27:12,020 --> 00:27:13,820
Bai Sha, the younger generation will in time surpass us!

650
00:27:14,140 --> 00:27:14,740
This Hu Shi

651
00:27:14,780 --> 00:27:16,580
is too important for our "Youth Magazine."

652
00:27:16,620 --> 00:27:17,580
Must grab him!

653
00:27:17,620 --> 00:27:18,580
Oh Zhong Fu,

654
00:27:20,060 --> 00:27:20,940
in this time and age,

655
00:27:21,060 --> 00:27:24,180
it's not easy to find a genius

656
00:27:24,820 --> 00:27:26,380
who can catch your eye.

657
00:27:27,260 --> 00:27:29,020
Though don't get too hung up on it.

658
00:27:29,060 --> 00:27:31,740
This guy is a doctoral student in the United States,

659
00:27:31,780 --> 00:27:33,580
and a disciple of Professor Dewey.

660
00:27:33,620 --> 00:27:35,380
As if you can grab him just by saying so.

661
00:27:35,660 --> 00:27:36,740
This guy lives in the United States.

662
00:27:36,900 --> 00:27:38,340
Whether he can even come back is an issue.

663
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:39,940
No, no. This I can guarantee.

664
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:42,300
He will definitely return to China after completing his studies.

665
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:43,980
How can one be sure?

666
00:27:45,580 --> 00:27:46,620
This guy, Hu Shi,

667
00:27:47,540 --> 00:27:49,180
is a filial son.

668
00:27:49,380 --> 00:27:50,900
Before he went abroad to study,

669
00:27:51,060 --> 00:27:53,900
his mother arranged a marriage for him.

670
00:27:54,060 --> 00:27:56,060
His mother can't wait to get a grandson.

671
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:58,700
So she writes him letters every few days

672
00:27:58,860 --> 00:28:01,580
telling him to come back after he finishes his studies to get married.

673
00:28:01,740 --> 00:28:03,340
He would not dare to disobey his mother.

674
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:05,260
This person is really too wonderful.

675
00:28:05,460 --> 00:28:06,460
His thinking is wonderful.

676
00:28:06,900 --> 00:28:07,140
What?

677
00:28:07,180 --> 00:28:07,880
Grab him!

678
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:10,580
Grab him as soon as he comes back.

679
00:28:26,300 --> 00:28:27,220
Junman!

680
00:28:27,820 --> 00:28:28,860
Here, let me.

681
00:28:34,580 --> 00:28:36,060
Why is your cough so bad?

682
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:36,860
You took your medicine?

683
00:28:37,300 --> 00:28:38,660
I did. It's not effective.

684
00:28:38,660 --> 00:28:40,020
It's not effective?

685
00:28:40,940 --> 00:28:42,060
You have to keep taking it.

686
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:43,540
How can the medicine work if you don't keep taking it?

687
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:45,340
I've finished it.

688
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:46,780
But there were no results.

689
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:48,860
You've finished it.

690
00:28:50,820 --> 00:28:51,980
Ok, alright.

691
00:28:52,020 --> 00:28:53,300
Don't work any more.

692
00:28:53,420 --> 00:28:55,340
Go rest in the house.

693
00:28:55,460 --> 00:28:56,660
Let me sit here for a bit.

694
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:57,340
Get some air.

695
00:29:00,780 --> 00:29:02,700
Then wait. I will go buy medicine.

696
00:29:04,100 --> 00:29:05,580
You don't need to go.

697
00:29:05,780 --> 00:29:06,940
The drawer has long run out of money.

698
00:29:06,980 --> 00:29:08,740
The money you gave me last month is all used up.

699
00:29:08,820 --> 00:29:10,260
It's an old problem.

700
00:29:10,540 --> 00:29:11,260
It'll pass.

701
00:29:11,700 --> 00:29:13,340
Don't worry. I'm not dying.

702
00:29:14,580 --> 00:29:15,340
Gao Junman!

703
00:29:16,100 --> 00:29:16,900
Don't work anymore!

704
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:19,140
No one's dying if the firewood's not chopped.

705
00:29:19,420 --> 00:29:20,300
Go inside and rest.

706
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:22,140
Wait for me.

707
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:28,140
No one's dying if the firewood's not chopped.

708
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:30,660
Can't cook if the firewood's not chopped!

709
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:46,220
Zhong Fu,

710
00:29:46,260 --> 00:29:48,060
why are you here in such a heavy rain?

711
00:29:48,340 --> 00:29:49,220
Just dropping by.

712
00:29:49,940 --> 00:29:51,220
Pour your own tea if you want.

713
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:56,140
Those the accounts?

714
00:30:01,260 --> 00:30:02,420
So today,

715
00:30:03,100 --> 00:30:04,940
I ran around to collect the money.

716
00:30:05,540 --> 00:30:08,380
To date, our "Youth Magazine"

717
00:30:08,620 --> 00:30:11,420
has sold 2000 copies in total,

718
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:13,380
breaking even.

719
00:30:13,900 --> 00:30:15,540
The principal has basically been recouped.

720
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:19,580
That's great.

721
00:30:21,900 --> 00:30:23,620
That's a good thing, right?

722
00:30:26,700 --> 00:30:27,860
Mengzou,

723
00:30:28,980 --> 00:30:30,300
My uh...

724
00:30:30,340 --> 00:30:32,020
This issue's payment for uh,

725
00:30:32,060 --> 00:30:33,020
for my editorial.

726
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:36,180
Is that included in the capital?

727
00:30:36,220 --> 00:30:37,620
I'm calculating the big accounts.

728
00:30:37,660 --> 00:30:39,860
Haven't had a chance yet to take you into consideration.

729
00:30:40,380 --> 00:30:42,340
Hold on, you have to take me into consideration as well.

730
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:44,060
If your capital has been recouped

731
00:30:44,260 --> 00:30:45,780
then shouldn't the payment for my editorial

732
00:30:45,940 --> 00:30:48,460
be given back to me?

733
00:30:50,300 --> 00:30:53,940
Alright, then let me take you into consideration right now.

734
00:30:54,660 --> 00:30:55,980
Let me see,

735
00:30:57,020 --> 00:31:00,580
Your manuscript fee, editorial fee

736
00:31:00,860 --> 00:31:02,460
added together

737
00:31:02,780 --> 00:31:05,380
is 138 silver dollars.

738
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:08,140
However, you've asked three times for an advance.

739
00:31:08,420 --> 00:31:10,100
The first time, for 4 silver dollars.

740
00:31:10,380 --> 00:31:12,060
The second time, also for 4 silver dollars.

741
00:31:12,260 --> 00:31:14,220
The third time, for 10 silver dollars.

742
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:15,900
18 all together.

743
00:31:16,060 --> 00:31:18,100
138 minus 18

744
00:31:18,300 --> 00:31:19,100
So you should get

745
00:31:19,140 --> 00:31:22,540
120 silver dollars, correct?

746
00:31:22,900 --> 00:31:24,420
I'll give it to you right now.

747
00:31:28,020 --> 00:31:29,380
Fifty.

748
00:31:31,620 --> 00:31:33,380
One hundred.

749
00:31:33,380 --> 00:31:35,140
One twenty.

750
00:31:35,340 --> 00:31:36,140
Take it.

751
00:31:36,700 --> 00:31:38,220
I borrowed money three times.

752
00:31:38,580 --> 00:31:41,140
Two $4 and one $10.

753
00:31:41,460 --> 00:31:42,780
Why don't I have any impression of this?

754
00:31:42,940 --> 00:31:44,860
These matters, you don't need to think over it.

755
00:31:45,020 --> 00:31:46,380
These are the matters I'll look after.

756
00:31:46,420 --> 00:31:47,580
As for you, great thinker

757
00:31:47,980 --> 00:31:50,100
just unhesitatingly let out your brilliance.

758
00:31:50,140 --> 00:31:51,060
Zhong Fu,

759
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:53,060
you say, this Yuan Shikai,

760
00:31:53,460 --> 00:31:56,060
his determination to be the emperor

761
00:31:56,580 --> 00:31:58,460
makes the heavens angry and causes people to resent.

762
00:31:58,660 --> 00:32:01,220
This authority, right now also has no time

763
00:32:01,420 --> 00:32:02,660
to deal with the revolutionaries.

764
00:32:03,140 --> 00:32:04,580
As soon as the current political situation starts to ease

765
00:32:04,740 --> 00:32:05,900
this business opportunity, it will come.

766
00:32:06,060 --> 00:32:08,620
I want to seize onto the opportunity, go out and raise capital.

767
00:32:08,980 --> 00:32:10,980
With your great persona, you will have a lot of acquaintances.

768
00:32:11,140 --> 00:32:13,060
Bring over more people with money to invest.

769
00:32:13,300 --> 00:32:15,580
This magazine of ours, maybe it will resume operations.

770
00:32:15,740 --> 00:32:17,220
Alright. No problem.

771
00:32:17,380 --> 00:32:19,540
You're responsible for finding people, I'll show up personally.

772
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:20,980
As long as the magazine can be managed well,

773
00:32:21,220 --> 00:32:23,100
whatever you have me do is fine.

774
00:32:23,140 --> 00:32:25,620
Uncle Wang.

775
00:32:25,820 --> 00:32:29,340
You've come back.

776
00:32:30,860 --> 00:32:31,940
Dad.

777
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:35,340
Why have you come back so early today?

778
00:32:35,380 --> 00:32:36,940
It's raining today, impossible to work.

779
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:40,580
Mengzou

780
00:32:40,660 --> 00:32:43,140
This... Yannian and Qiaonian doing editing here,

781
00:32:43,460 --> 00:32:45,140
isn't it that they should have pay too?

782
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:47,460
I gave it to them, Yannian didn't want it.

783
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:49,220
Speaking about this pay,

784
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:51,940
it's made up for in my accommodation fees here.

785
00:32:53,540 --> 00:32:54,860
I want to properly discuss with you,

786
00:32:54,900 --> 00:32:56,260
these two children's matters.

787
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:58,460
In the daytime, they are working at the port.

788
00:32:58,660 --> 00:33:00,460
At night, they come over to my place to be editors.

789
00:33:00,660 --> 00:33:02,180
And they still need to learn French.

790
00:33:02,420 --> 00:33:04,100
Wouldn't you say these two children are too tired

791
00:33:04,300 --> 00:33:08,420
That is to say, the two brothers living costs right now,

792
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:11,700
all depends on the salary from working at the port.

793
00:33:11,940 --> 00:33:12,940
That's right.

794
00:33:13,100 --> 00:33:15,260
I have also heard, at the port they

795
00:33:15,420 --> 00:33:17,060
extended the working time.

796
00:33:17,260 --> 00:33:18,860
I quietly asked Qiaonian

797
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:20,260
what's going on?

798
00:33:20,460 --> 00:33:23,580
He said it's for getting the tuition to learn French.

799
00:33:24,820 --> 00:33:26,340
You say, what to do?

800
00:33:27,540 --> 00:33:29,260
This child, right now

801
00:33:29,500 --> 00:33:31,140
when his body is still growing.

802
00:33:31,300 --> 00:33:33,540
If he's like this, wouldn't his body break down?

803
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:35,180
You say, what to do with this?

804
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:38,780
Those two, if they didn't want the editing pay,

805
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:40,500
you should give it me.

806
00:33:41,180 --> 00:33:42,420
I am his father.

807
00:33:42,580 --> 00:33:44,340
It should be me... Receiving it...

808
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:47,020
It should be normal too, right?

809
00:33:47,740 --> 00:33:49,220
What! This is...

810
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:50,980
That's another matter!

811
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:52,980
Didn't I already tell you?

812
00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:54,900
Yannian had the pay

813
00:33:55,100 --> 00:33:57,220
included it in the accommodation fees here.

814
00:33:57,460 --> 00:33:58,780
You still say your son and you are very similar,

815
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:00,340
not even a little similar.

816
00:34:00,580 --> 00:34:01,980
He, give him money and he doesn't want it.

817
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:05,020
You here, keep going on and on with me.

818
00:34:21,700 --> 00:34:23,300
This is 50 silver dollars.

819
00:34:25,140 --> 00:34:26,860
100 silver dollars.

820
00:34:29,340 --> 00:34:29,780
This is 20.

821
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:30,740
Dad, what are you giving me so much..

822
00:34:30,780 --> 00:34:31,700
Listen to me.

823
00:34:31,740 --> 00:34:34,580
This money, I give it to you two brothers to pay tuition.

824
00:34:34,980 --> 00:34:35,900
Understand?

825
00:34:36,660 --> 00:34:37,260
Quickly go.

826
00:34:43,060 --> 00:34:45,420
Zhong Fu.

827
00:34:45,580 --> 00:34:46,620
You already gave it.

828
00:34:51,540 --> 00:34:52,900
Mengzou.

829
00:34:53,260 --> 00:34:54,500
You say, just now

